  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}Aigis!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}I'm sorry... I...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}I... remember everything...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}I remember who I am... Who he is...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}{f 4 2}-san...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}I know why I wanted to be by your side.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}I'm sorry. I failed...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="SEL_004_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}What happened?]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}It's going to be okay.]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Save your energy.]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 7 30 203 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}I'm... sorry...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0003"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}You have no reason to apologize.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}You!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 12 0 0}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}Ryoji-kun?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}Wait, what're you doing here!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Aigis!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MND_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Aigis is no longer moving...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}She appears to have stopped functioning...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0007"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 2 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}What is going on...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 17 0 0}It's... all my fault.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0007"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 2 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}Wha— You did this!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}Hold on, Akihiko. He's not showing any signs of aggression.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}Now tell us...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}Who—or what—are you?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="17" name="MSG_017_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}Turns out, I'm not so different from the creatures you call Shadows.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="18" name="MSG_018_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}You're a Shadow!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="19" name="MSG_019_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}I'm more than just an ordinary Shadow.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}I'm the Appriser, born from the union of the twelve Arcana.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="20" name="MSG_020_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 26 0 0}The Appriser?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="21" name="MSG_021_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 0 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 27 0 0}I remember everything now.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 28 0 0}{f 4 23 0 221 3 25 25}The terrifying truth about the Shadows... and about me.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 10 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 29 0 0}{f 4 23 0 221 10 25 25}I can't... It's all so hard to believe.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="22" name="MSG_022_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 30 0 0}You know the "truth" about the Shadows?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="23" name="MSG_023_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 31 0 0}I do.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="24" name="MSG_024_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0007"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 4 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 32 0 0}What!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="25" name="MSG_025_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 33 0 0}The Shadows are here to facilitate the rebirth of the maternal being.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 34 0 0}As for the Appriser...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 35 0 0}It draws the maternal being to it, allowing her to awaken.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="26" name="MSG_026_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 36 0 0}And the Appriser... That's you?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="27" name="MSG_027_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 37 0 0}That's right.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="28" name="MSG_028_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 3 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 38 0 0}This "maternal being"... What is it?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="29" name="MSG_029_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 39 0 0}She's on a level of her own. No words in our language can describe her.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="30" name="MSG_030_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 40 0 0}Ten years ago, a man collected hordes of Shadows and contained them in a laboratory.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 41 0 0}That's where I was born.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 42 0 0}But the unification was interrupted, and I awoke before I was complete.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 43 0 0}After that, Aigis took me down, and I returned the favor.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="31" name="MSG_031_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 44 0 0}Aigis!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 45 0 0}Is this for real, Ryoji?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="32" name="MSG_032_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 46 0 0}She knew she couldn't destroy me completely.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 47 0 0}So out of desperation, she sealed me within a child who just happened to be nearby.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 48 0 0}That child grew up carrying me inside him. And by some twist of fate, he later made his way back here.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 49 0 0}He even transferred to your school.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="33" name="MSG_033_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 50 0 0}A transfer student? You don't mean...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="34" name="MSG_034_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 51 0 0}That's right. {f 4 2}.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 52 0 0}I've lived inside him for a long time.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="35" name="SEL_035_0_0" type="Selection">
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Inside me?]]></Option>
    <Option><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}......]]></Option>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="36" name="MSG_036_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 2 3 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 53 0 0}B-But how...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="37" name="MSG_037_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 54 0 0}And when his Persona awakened, the twelve Shadows did as well.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 55 0 0}...All in order to become one with me.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="38" name="MSG_038_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 56 0 0}Ryoji, you're the Appriser? And you were inside of him!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0004"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 2 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 57 0 0}{f 4 23 0 3 2 25 25}How the hell do you expect us to just believe all that!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="39" name="MSG_039_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 58 0 0}It's... all my fault.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 59 0 0}I'm sorry.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0005"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 221 10 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 60 0 0}{f 4 23 0 221 10 25 25}But there's more... I need... to tell you...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="40" name="MSG_040_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0006"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 6 4 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 61 0 0}Ryoji-kun![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="41" name="MND_041_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}It seems he fell unconscious.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="42" name="MSG_042_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 62 0 0}He's completely worn out.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 63 0 0}Let's let him rest for now. Aigis needs us, too.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0008"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 0 52 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 64 0 0}We'll pick up where we left off after that.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="43" name="MND_043_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}What I just heard was shocking...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Ryoji lived inside me for ten years, waiting[n]to make contact with the twelve Shadows...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}Then does that mean the boy named[n]Pharos was actually Ryoji all along?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}So many questions remain unanswered.[n]However, Ryoji is unconscious...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}......[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="FFFF"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}We took Ryoji and Aigis home, the[n]air surrounding us frigid and somber.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
